{"tid":1801923,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【信心滿滿】如新蝙蝠俠不獲讚賞 羅拔：我會轉拍咸片","createTime":"2019-12-29T04:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T07:32:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75d1062fe2d71df58fe6eeacb5bb58949baf1c95","tid":1801923,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"導演麥里夫斯（Matt Reeves）執導，《吸血新世紀》（Twilight）男星羅拔柏迪臣（Robert Pattinson）主演的新版蝙蝠俠已正在籌備當中，而羅拔亦極有信心，最近更笑言如今集蝙蝠俠不獲讚賞，就轉行拍咸片！<br />\n其實自從電影公司公佈，羅拔柏迪臣將會成為蝙蝠俠之後，已惹來劣評如潮。羅拔亦為此事心有不甘，在最近之訪問中更回應事件：「要講大家都有期望的電影，我記得這種感覺。每當你講任何東西，人們都會說：『啊！你這個白癡！』喂，我還未開始講！」對於觀眾都質疑他能否演好蝙蝠俠，他就指：「世上沒有一個人比我對我自己更嚴厲，因此我不需要擔心其他人怎樣想。」他更笑指，若大家不喜歡這個新蝙蝠俠：「我會轉拍咸片，但是會在獨立戲院放映的咸片。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191229/large/1577591585_3210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577591585_3210.jpg&h=409dcd7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191229/60428323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428323&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=13ffcd49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60428323&h=ab5dd9a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191229/60428323</a>"},{"pid":"33772c14a7f6d66cfe1628d47049ed3f634053ec","tid":1801923,"uid":46587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"拍開吸血新世紀呢D咸片大把經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f02dc1247449798211ed46e2c1749a9b0cf0dc9","tid":1801923,"uid":25327,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"借d意轉型<img src=\"/assets/fac